# Only PKGBUILD and .SRCINFO are tracked here. `makepkg` runs in-place in this
# dir (see the README install steps), so everything else is build scratch —
# src/, pkg/, the git+ source checkouts, the built package, downloaded tarballs.
# Whitelist rather than blacklist so new deps can't leak a checkout into a commit.
*
!.gitignore
!PKGBUILD
!.SRCINFO
